
# Ecommerce Platforms

## Ecommerce Platform Object
Represents a ecommerce platform object.

```json
{
  "id": "eplat_5lu3ll5pgpumqvl",
  "name": "Shopify",
  "key": "shopify",
  "type": "PREDEFINED"
}
```

### Attributes
Field | Type | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
id | string | Unique identifier for the object.
name | string | Name for ecommerce platform.
key | string | Human readable key to uniquely identify platform.
type | enum ([Platform Type](#ecommerce-platforms-enums-platform-type)) | Type for this platform.


## Enums
List of available enum types under this resource.

### Platform Type
Value | Description
--------- | -------
PREDEFINED | Predefined
CUSTOM | Custom


## Retrieve Ecommerce Platform

> Example Request

```shell
curl https://api.onvoard.com/v2/ecommerce-platforms/eplat_5lu3ll5pgpumqvl \
-H 'X-API-Key: {API_KEY}'
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "id": "eplat_5lu3ll5pgpumqvl",
  "name": "Shopify",
  "key": "shopify",
  "type": "PREDEFINED"
}
```

Retrieve ecommerce platform with given ID.

### HTTP Request
`GET https://api.onvoard.com/v2/ecommerce-platforms/:ecommerce_platform_id`

### Returns
Ecommerce Platform object if valid ID was provided.


## List all Ecommerce Platforms

> Example Request

```shell
curl https://api.onvoard.com/v2/ecommerce-platforms \
-H 'X-API-Key: {API_KEY}'
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "num_platforms": 1,
  "num_pages": 1,
  "current_page": 1,
  "results": [{
    "id": "eplat_5lu3ll5pgpumqvl",
    "name": "Shopify",
    "key": "shopify",
    "type": "PREDEFINED"
  }]
}
```

List all ecommerce platforms user have access to.

### HTTP Request
`GET https://api.onvoard.com/v2/ecommerce-platforms`

### Returns
List of ecommerce platforms objects.

### Arguments
Field | Type | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
keyword | string | Filter by specific keyword.
page | integer | Traverse to specific page. Page index starts from `1`.
page_size | integer | Number of platforms you want to return for each page. Can be from `1` to `100`. Default is `10`.



